com.mesosfer

Class MesosferConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mesosfer.MesosferConfig

  • public class MesosferConfig
extends Object
    The MesosferConfig is a local representation of configuration data that can be set from the Mesosfer dashboard.

        public static void getInBackground(ConfigCallback callback)

        Parameters:
